name: 丽莎·纳索
introduction: Lisa Naso is an actor and writer based in New York City. Lisa grew up in Long Island, where they attended Long Island High School for the Arts as a musical theater major. They graduated with a BFA in Acting from Point Park University. Lisa performed in regional theater and on a national tour before moving to New York to pursue film acting. In 2023, Lisa won Best Actor at the First Frame International Film Festival in New York City.
